    "body": "In the future, SSZ, BLS-js, Gossipsub-js. The reasoning is we will have these separate repos as their own packages but managing all of them will be a hassle as this gets bigger. The main reasons for why we wouldn't want to monorepo this, in my opinion, is for maintenance and onboarding others.\r\n\r\nIf we do decide we don't want to monorepo then this tool is not useful. I just want to start this discussion early so that we can easily add appropriate documentation.",
